entries.journal_entry_description: Collect flawless mouf incisors from vicious moufs.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Tripp wants you to collect 18 flawless mouf incisors. Hunt vicious moufs to obtain them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have collected the mouf incisors. Now return to Tripp at the main Rodian hunting camp.
